    ["QUI conflicts with another addon"] = "QUI 與另一個插件衝突",
    ["QUI includes many small quality-of-life improvements: auto-repair, auto-sell junk, improved tooltips, chat enhancements, a crosshair overlay, skyriding helpers, and more."] = "QUI 包含許多小型生活品質改進：自動修理、自動出售垃圾、改良工具提示、聊天增強、準星覆蓋、空騎輔助等。",
    ["QUI is a full UI suite built around QUI 3 systems: custom unit and group frames, Cooldown Manager viewers, action bar styling, anchoring and layout tools, profile import/export, skinning, and quality-of-life modules - all configurable from one options panel."] = "QUI 是一套完整 UI 工具組，以 QUI 3 系統為核心：自訂單位與隊伍框架、Cooldown Manager 檢視、動作條樣式、錨定與佈局工具、設定檔匯入／匯出、外觀套用，以及生活品質模組 - 全部都可從同一個選項面板設定。",
    ["QUI is designed to work alongside other addons, but conflicts can occur with addons that modify the same frames. Try disabling the conflicting addon to isolate the issue, then report it on GitHub with both addon names."] = "QUI 設計上可與其他插件並存，但若插件修改同一批框架，仍可能發生衝突。請嘗試停用衝突插件以隔離問題，然後在 GitHub 回報，並附上兩個插件名稱。",
    ["QUI options (/qui)"] = "QUI 選項（/qui）",
    ["QUI replaces the default player, target, focus, party, and raid frames with custom-styled versions. Each unit type can be configured independently with health/power bars, name text, portraits, and aura displays."] = "QUI 以自訂樣式版本取代預設的玩家、目標、焦點、隊伍與團隊框架。每種單位類型都可獨立設定，包含生命／能量條、名稱文字、肖像與光環顯示。",
    ["QUI skins many Blizzard frames to match the addon's visual style. The autohide system lets you hide specific UI elements (like gryphons, XP bar, or micro menu) to clean up your screen."] = "QUI 會為許多 Blizzard 框架套用外觀，使其符合插件的視覺風格。自動隱藏系統可讓你隱藏特定 UI 元素（例如 gryphons、XP 條或微型選單）以讓畫面更整潔。",
    ["QUI styles and customizes your action bars with consistent appearance, keybind text, and optional per-bar overrides for size, spacing, and visibility."] = "QUI 以一致的外觀、按鍵綁定文字，以及可選的每條覆寫（大小、間距、可見性）來樣式化並自訂你的動作條。",
    ["QUI styles the minimap with custom borders and shape options, and provides data text panels that display useful information like FPS, latency, gold, and more."] = "QUI 以自訂邊框與形狀選項樣式化迷你地圖，並提供資料文字面板顯示 FPS、延遲、金幣等實用資訊。",
    ["QUI's bag takeover. Mirrors the Bags row on the Module Addons page: enabling loads the module (live when possible), disabling hands bags back to Blizzard — a UI reload is prompted for a clean handoff. Everything below applies live while the module is enabled."] = "QUI 的背包接管。與模組插件頁面的 Bags 列相同：啟用會載入模組（若可能會即時載入），停用則把背包控制權交還 Blizzard - 為了乾淨交接會提示重新載入 UI。下方所有設定在模組啟用時會即時生效。",
    ["QUI's chat takeover. Enabled: chat is captured and rendered in QUI's own display. Disabled: QUI leaves chat completely stock."] = "QUI 的聊天接管。啟用：聊天會被擷取並以 QUI 自己的顯示呈現。停用：QUI 完全使用原生聊天。",
