    ["Replace All"] = "全部取代",
    ["Replace Blizzard's default UI fonts with the QUI default font so the whole client shares the same typography."] = "以 QUI 預設字型取代 Blizzard 的預設 UI 字型，讓整個客戶端共用相同字體。",
    ["Replace Blizzard's party and raid frames with QUI group frames. Requires a UI reload to take effect."] = "以 QUI 群組框架取代 Blizzard 的隊伍與團隊框架。需要重新載入 UI 才會生效。",
    ["Replace Default Prey Indicator"] = "取代預設獵物指示器",
