    ["Replace every setting in profile '%1$s' with this import string?"] = "要以此匯入字串取代設定檔「%1$s」中的每一項設定嗎？",
    ["Replace verbose channel tags like [Guild] with compact labels like [G] in chat output."] = "將像 [Guild] 這類冗長的頻道標記在聊天輸出中替換成像 [G] 這類簡短標籤。",
    ["Replace your current profile with every setting from this string?"] = "要以此字串中的每一項設定取代你目前的設定檔嗎？",
    ["Report Edit Mode state and the most recent ADDON_ACTION_BLOCKED events. Run after a frame-positioning action that didn't take effect."] = "回報編輯模式狀態與最近的 ADDON_ACTION_BLOCKED 事件。在未生效的框架位置操作後執行。",
