    ["Show Zones"] = "顯示區域",
    ["Show a 3D unit portrait next to this frame. Side, size, gap, and border style are set below."] = "在此框架旁顯示 3D 單位頭像。側邊、大小、間距與邊框樣式在下方設定。",
    ["Show a Sell Junk button in the bag window while a merchant is open."] = "商人開啟時，在背包視窗中顯示出售垃圾按鈕。",
    ["Show a Whirling Surge cooldown icon on the skyriding bar."] = "在空中飛行條上顯示旋湧冷卻圖示。",
    ["Show a brief explanation of each setting when you hover over it in this panel."] = "在本面板中將滑鼠停在設定上時，顯示每個設定的簡短說明。",
    ["Show a bright edge on the active recharge slice for spells with charges."] = "為有充能的法術在目前重新充能切片上顯示亮邊。",
    ["Show a bright spark at the leading edge of the filled portion of the bar."] = "在條列填滿區的前緣顯示亮點。",
    ["Show a classification icon next to elite, rare, rare-elite, and boss NPCs on this unit frame."] = "在此單位框架上，於精英、稀有、稀有精英與首領 NPC 旁顯示分類圖示。",
    ["Show a clickable Great Vault shortcut anchored relative to the minimap."] = "顯示一個可點擊的大祕境寶庫捷徑，錨定於小地圖相對位置。",
    ["Show a colored border around the rotation assist icon."] = "在旋轉輔助圖示周圍顯示彩色邊框。",
    ["Show a consumables window listing food, flasks, weapon enchants, runes, and healthstones based on the triggers below."] = "顯示一個補給品視窗，依下方觸發條件列出食物、藥劑、武器附魔、符文與治療石。",
    ["Show a count next to each missing buff indicating how many group members are missing it."] = "在每個缺少的增益旁顯示數量，表示有多少隊伍成員缺少它。",
    ["Show a crown icon on the party/raid leader and a flag icon on raid assistants."] = "在隊長/團隊隊長上顯示皇冠圖示，在團隊助理上顯示旗幟圖示。",
    ["Show a customizable reticle at the center of your screen for aiming and combat feedback."] = "在畫面中央顯示可自訂瞄準點，用於瞄準與戰鬥回饋。",
    ["Show a dedicated icon strip for active defensive cooldowns on this frame."] = "在此框架上顯示專用的防禦冷卻圖示條。",
    ["Show a draggable preview frame so you can position the distance bracket display."] = "顯示可拖曳的預覽框架，以便你放置距離括號顯示。",
    ["Show a footer row on the bag window with the currencies enabled below."] = "在背包視窗底部顯示一列貨幣，列出下方啟用的貨幣。",
    ["Show a list of available hunts when you interact with a hunt table NPC, so you can pick the best prey at a glance."] = "與狩獵桌 NPC 互動時，顯示可用狩獵清單，讓你一眼挑選最佳獵物。",
    ["Show a per-slot item level number on each piece of gear in the inspect window."] = "在檢視視窗中的每件裝備上顯示每個欄位的物品等級數值。",
    ["Show a portrait next to each frame."] = "在每個框架旁顯示頭像。",
    ["Show a power bar below the health bar on this frame."] = "在此框架上於生命值條下方顯示能量條。",
    ["Show a quality indicator on profession items placed on action bars."] = "在動作條上的專業物品顯示品質指示器。",
    ["Show a small durability bar on each slot overlay that has durability damage."] = "在有耐久度損耗的欄位疊加層上顯示小型耐久度條。",
    ["Show a small gear icon on items that belong to a saved equipment set (live bag and bank views)."] = "在屬於已儲存裝備套裝的物品上顯示小齒輪圖示（背包與銀行即時檢視）。",
    ["Show a text label on the player frame naming your current stance, shapeshift form, or aura."] = "在玩家框架上顯示文字標籤，標示你目前的姿態、變形型態或光環。",
    ["Show a tooltip line for attackable enemies that do not contribute forces."] = "為不會提供進度的可攻擊敵人顯示一行提示文字。",
    ["Show a tooltip with class color, total, per-second, and percent when hovering a row."] = "滑鼠指向某列時，顯示職業顏色、總量、每秒與百分比的提示。",
    ["Show an alert when the prey enters an ambushable state so you can position for the takedown."] = "當獵物進入可伏擊狀態時顯示警示，以便你佔位收割。",
    ["Show an icon for the active stance/form next to the text."] = "在文字旁顯示目前姿態/型態圖示。",
    ["Show average equipped item level on player tooltips. Remote players may populate after a short inspect delay."] = "在玩家提示中顯示平均裝備物品等級。遠端玩家可能在短暫檢視延遲後才會填入。",
    ["Show bar border"] = "顯示條邊框",
    ["Show bar text"] = "顯示條文字",
    ["Show buffs Blizzard's raid frames would show."] = "顯示 Blizzard 團隊框架會顯示的增益。",
    ["Show button bar for this frame"] = "顯示此框架的按鈕列",
    ["Show colored gem dots indicating how many gem slots the item has and whether each is filled."] = "顯示彩色寶石點，標示物品的寶石欄位數量及是否已鑲嵌。",
    ["Show companion frames for pets alongside the main group."] = "顯示寵物同伴框架，與主群組並列。",
    ["Show debuffs Blizzard's raid frames would show."] = "顯示 Blizzard 團隊框架會顯示的減益。",
    ["Show each visible enemy's forces contribution next to its nameplate."] = "在每個可見敵人的姓名板旁顯示其進度貢獻。",
    ["Show how many of an item you own across characters, bank, mail, and more on item tooltips. 'While Shift Held' shows the counts only while Shift is down."] = "在物品提示中顯示你跨角色、銀行、郵件等持有的該物品數量。「按住 Shift 時」只在按住 Shift 時顯示數量。",
    ["Show item level and enchant overlays on inspected players. Requires a reload to take effect."] = "在被檢視玩家身上顯示物品等級與附魔覆蓋層。需要重新載入才會生效。",
    ["Show keybind overlays on action buttons"] = "在動作按鈕上顯示快捷鍵覆蓋層",
    ["Show numeric vigor count on the bar."] = "在條上顯示數字活力次數。",
    ["Show on Hover"] = "滑鼠懸停時顯示",
    ["Show on Melee Swings"] = "近戰揮擊時顯示",
    ["Show only big-defensive buffs (Aspect of the Turtle, Divine Shield, Ice Block, etc.). Patch 12.0.1+."] = "只顯示大型防禦增益（龜殼、聖盾術、寒冰屏障等）。12.0.1+。",
    ["Show only buffs flagged as raid-relevant for your class — typically the ones you'd track on a raid frame."] = "只顯示被標記為與團隊相關、且屬於你職業的增益，通常是你會在團隊框架上追蹤的那些。",
    ["Show only buffs that cannot be cancelled — flasks, food, world buffs, gear procs, and similar. Mutually exclusive with Only Cancellable."] = "只顯示無法取消的增益 - 藥劑、食物、世界增益、裝備觸發等。與「只顯示可取消」互斥。",
    ["Show only buffs you applied yourself. Hides everything cast on you by others."] = "只顯示你自己施放的增益。隱藏其他人對你施放的一切。",
    ["Show only buffs you applied."] = "只顯示你自己施放的增益。",
    ["Show only buffs you can right-click off."] = "只顯示你可右鍵移除的增益。",
    ["Show only buffs you can right-click to cancel. Excludes most consumables, talents, and gear procs. Mutually exclusive with Only Persistent."] = "只顯示你可右鍵取消的增益。排除大多數消耗品、天賦與裝備觸發。與「只顯示持續存在」互斥。",
    ["Show only buffs you cannot right-click off."] = "只顯示你無法右鍵移除的增益。",
    ["Show only crowd-control effects (stuns, fears, roots, etc.). Patch 12.0.1+."] = "只顯示控制效果（昏迷、恐懼、定身等）。12.0.1+。",
    ["Show only debuffs flagged as raid-relevant — typically what raid frames would surface."] = "只顯示被標記為與團隊相關的減益，通常是團隊框架會顯示的內容。",
    ["Show only debuffs whose dispel type your class can remove. Patch 12.0.1+."] = "只顯示你職業可驅散類型的減益。12.0.1+。",
    ["Show only debuffs you applied — useful for DoT trackers and similar."] = "只顯示你施放的減益，對 DoT 追蹤器等很有用。",
    ["Show only debuffs you applied."] = "只顯示你施放的減益。",
    ["Show only spells flagged as important by C_Spell.IsSpellImportant. Patch 12.0.1+."] = "只顯示被 C_Spell.IsSpellImportant 標記為重要的法術。12.0.1+。",
    ["Show only while the buff is active. Hides the cooldown phase entirely."] = "只在增益有效時顯示。完全隱藏冷卻階段。",
    ["Show or hide the bag bar. Stays in sync with this element's enable toggle in Layout Mode."] = "顯示或隱藏背包列。與佈局模式中此元素的啟用開關保持同步。",
    ["Show or hide the micro menu. Stays in sync with this element's enable toggle in Layout Mode."] = "顯示或隱藏微型選單。與佈局模式中此元素的啟用開關保持同步。",
    ["Show or hide this action bar. Bars 2-8 can be individually disabled without affecting the pet or stance bars."] = "顯示或隱藏此動作列。第2-8列可單獨停用而不影響寵物或姿態列。",
    ["Show per-enemy forces contribution on M+ tooltips and nameplates."] = "在大祕境提示與姓名板上顯示每個敵人的進度貢獻。",
    ["Show realm names"] = "顯示伺服器名稱",
    ["Show remaining-time text on %1$s icons."] = "在 %1$s 圖示上顯示剩餘時間文字。",
    ["Show session separators"] = "顯示場次分隔線",
    ["Show small frames for group-member pets."] = "顯示隊伍成員寵物的小型框架。",
    ["Show stack counts on aura icons when the buff or debuff has multiple stacks."] = "當增益或減益有多層時，在光環圖示上顯示疊層數。",
    ["Show the %1$s button in the Micro Menu widget."] = "在快捷選單小工具中顯示 %1$s 按鈕。",
    ["Show the %1$s indicator on this unit frame."] = "在此單位框架上顯示 %1$s 指示器。",
    ["Show the '%s' button on this chat frame's button bar."] = "在此聊天框的按鈕列上顯示「%s」按鈕。",
    ["Show the Blizzard unit tooltip when hovering a group frame."] = "滑鼠停在團隊框架上時顯示 Blizzard 單位提示。",
    ["Show the Blizzard-rendered countdown number on each private-aura icon."] = "在每個私人光環圖示上顯示 Blizzard 渲染的倒數數字。",
    ["Show the LFG eye icon on a corner of the minimap while you're queued for a dungeon or raid."] = "排隊等待地城或團隊時，在小地圖角落顯示 LFG 眼睛圖示。",
    ["Show the QUI crosshair at the center of your screen. Useful for Dragonriding, action-camera play, and ranged classes."] = "在畫面中央顯示 QUI 準星。對龍飛行、動作視角與遠程職業很有用。",
    ["Show the QUI zone label above the minimap."] = "在小地圖上方顯示 QUI 地區標籤。",
    ["Show the XP, reputation, or honor numeric text on top of the bar."] = "在條上方顯示經驗、聲望或榮譽數值文字。",
    ["Show the ability tooltip when hovering an action button."] = "滑鼠懸停動作按鈕時顯示法術提示。",
    ["Show the active mount's name on mounted player tooltips."] = "在騎乘玩家提示中顯示目前坐騎名稱。",
    ["Show the active weekly affix icons on the timer panel."] = "在計時器面板上顯示本週詞綴圖示。",
    ["Show the bag-slot strip at the top of the bag window: your four bag slots plus the reagent bag slot. Drag a container onto a slot (or click with one on the cursor) to equip or swap it; click an equipped bag to pick it up."] = "顯示背包欄條位於背包視窗頂部：你的四個背包欄位加上材料包欄位。將容器拖到欄位上（或在游標上帶著它點擊）即可裝備或交換；點擊已裝備背包可將其拾起。",
    ["Show the boss/objective rows under the timer."] = "在計時器下方顯示首領/目標行。",
    ["Show the bound key text on each icon in this container."] = "在此容器中的每個圖示上顯示綁定按鍵文字。",
    ["Show the castbar for this unit."] = "顯示此單位的施法條。",
    ["Show the clockwise cooldown swipe animation on icons in this container."] = "在此容器中的圖示上顯示順時針冷卻掃動動畫。",
    ["Show the clockwise cooldown swipe over each private-aura icon."] = "在每個私人光環圖示上顯示順時針冷卻掃動。",
    ["Show the combat icon on the player frame while you're in combat."] = "在戰鬥中顯示玩家框架上的戰鬥圖示。",
    ["Show the consumables reminder when you resurrect inside an instance, to catch dropped flasks/food."] = "當你在副本內復活時顯示補給提醒，以補上掉失的藥劑/食物。",
    ["Show the consumables reminder when you zone into a dungeon."] = "當你進入地城時顯示補給提醒。",
    ["Show the consumables reminder when you zone into a raid."] = "當你進入團隊時顯示補給提醒。",
    ["Show the consumables reminder whenever a ready check is triggered."] = "每當觸發準備檢查時顯示補給提醒。",
    ["Show the cooldown swipe animation over private aura icons."] = "在私人光環圖示上顯示冷卻掃動動畫。",
    ["Show the current target's distance bracket as on-screen text."] = "以螢幕文字顯示目前目標的距離括號。",
    ["Show the current/next XP values and percent as text on top of the bar."] = "在條上方以文字顯示目前/下一級經驗值與百分比。",
    ["Show the custom buff frame managed by QUI."] = "顯示由 QUI 管理的自訂增益框架。",
    ["Show the custom debuff frame managed by QUI."] = "顯示由 QUI 管理的自訂減益框架。",
    ["Show the dark trough behind each row's colored fill."] = "在每列彩色填滿區後方顯示深色底槽。",
    ["Show the datatext panel anchored below the minimap."] = "顯示錨定在小地圖下方的資料文字面板。",
    ["Show the deaths counter and penalty time on the timer panel."] = "在計時器面板上顯示死亡計數與懲罰時間。",
    ["Show the enchant name on each inspect slot, or a missing-enchant marker if the slot has no enchant."] = "在每個檢視欄位顯示附魔名稱，若無附魔則顯示缺少附魔標記。",
    ["Show the enchant name on each slot, or a missing-enchant marker if the slot has no enchant."] = "在每個欄位顯示附魔名稱，若無附魔則顯示缺少附魔標記。",
    ["Show the enemy's count contribution when the value is available for Lua to inspect."] = "在 Lua 可檢視該值時，顯示敵人的進度貢獻。",
    ["Show the equipped item's name on each character panel slot overlay."] = "在角色面板每個欄位疊加層上顯示已裝備物品名稱。",
