    ["Status bar texture used to fill the prey tracker bar."] = "用於填充獵物追蹤條的狀態條材質。",
    ["Statusbar texture used for both skyriding bars. Supports any extra media packages you have available."] = "用於兩個天空飛行條的狀態條材質。支援你可用的任何額外媒體套件。",
    ["Statusbar texture used for the XP fill. Supports any extra media packages you have available."] = "用於經驗值填充的狀態條材質。支援你可用的任何額外媒體套件。",
    ["Statusbar texture used for the absorb overlay. Stripes or patterned textures make absorbs easier to read at a glance."] = "用於吸收覆蓋層的狀態條材質。條紋或圖樣材質更容易一眼看出吸收。",
    ["Statusbar texture used for the bar fill."] = "用於條填滿的狀態條材質。",
