    ["Stop the combat-end profiler and unwrap functions."] = "停止戰鬥結束分析器並解除包裝函式。",
    ["Store separate entry lists per specialization, so each spec shows a different set of tracked spells. The current list is swapped in on spec change."] = "按專精分開儲存條目清單，因此每個專精會顯示不同的追蹤法術集合。切換專精時會交換目前清單。",
