    ["Suppress all cooldown effects (swipe, overlay, flash) for this container, even on Blizzard-managed elements driven by the same icons."] = "抑制此容器的所有冷卻效果（掃動、覆蓋層、閃光），即使是由同一批圖示驅動的 Blizzard 管理元素也一樣。",
    ["Suppress all tooltips while you're in combat. Use the modifier key below to force-show them when needed."] = "戰鬥中抑制所有提示。需要時可用下方修飾鍵強制顯示。",
    ["Suppress entitlement and recruit-a-friend delivery toast notifications."] = "抑制資格與好友招募獎勵通知。",
