    ["Suppress the pulsing reminder on the talent microbutton that appears when unspent points are available."] = "當有未分配點數時，抑制天賦微型按鈕上的脈動提醒。",
    ["Suppress the red error messages printed above the action bar, such as Not Enough Mana or Spell Not Ready."] = "抑制動作條上方顯示的紅色錯誤訊息，例如法力不足或法術尚未就緒。",
