    ["Suppress the tutorial help tip callouts that Blizzard shows near talent and spellbook buttons."] = "抑制 Blizzard 在天賦與法術書按鈕附近顯示的教學提示。",
    ["Suppress the yellow info messages printed above the action bar, such as quest objective progress updates."] = "抑制動作條上方顯示的黃色資訊訊息，例如任務目標進度更新。",
    ["Suppress warband scene notification toasts."] = "抑制戰團場景通知快顯。",
    ["Swap the vigor bar color while Thrill of the Skies is active so the buff state is obvious."] = "當「天空之怒」啟用時交換活力條顏色，使增益狀態更明顯。",
