    ["Text shown on the button when no icon is set."] = "未設定圖示時按鈕上顯示的文字。",
    ["Texture"] = "材質",
    ["Texture path for an icon-style button — e.g. Interface/Icons/Spell_Holy_HolyBolt or any registered AddOn texture path. Leave blank to render as a text button."] = "圖示式按鈕的材質路徑，例如 Interface/Icons/Spell_Holy_HolyBolt，或任何已註冊的 AddOn 材質路徑。留空則以文字按鈕方式呈現。",
    ["Thalassian Resistance (Vers)"] = "撒拉斯抵抗（全能）",
    ["The CDM swipe overlay shows remaining cooldown time visually on each icon."] = "CDM 掃動覆蓋層會在每個圖示上以視覺方式顯示剩餘冷卻時間。",
    ["The Cooldown Manager displays your ability cooldowns as icon bars near your character. It integrates with Blizzard's CooldownViewer system and adds custom tracking, glow effects, and swipe overlays."] = "冷卻管理器會在你的角色附近以圖示條顯示技能冷卻。它整合 Blizzard 的 CooldownViewer 系統，並加入自訂追蹤、發光效果與掃動覆蓋層。",
    ["The Cooldown Manager icons aren't appearing"] = "冷卻管理器圖示沒有出現",
    ["The Cooldown Manager powers QUI's essential and utility cooldown viewers, buff trackers, and tracked bars. Use |cff60A5FA/qui cdm|r to open the CDM Spell Composer and control what gets tracked, then use the Cooldown Manager tab for appearance, glows, keybind text, and custom-entry behavior. If you need Blizzard's viewer settings panel itself, use |cff60A5FA/cdm|r."] = "冷卻管理器支援 QUI 的核心與實用冷卻檢視器、增益追蹤器與追蹤條。使用 |cff60A5FA/qui cdm|r 開啟 CDM 法術編輯器並控制追蹤內容，接著在冷卻管理器分頁設定外觀、發光、快捷鍵文字與自訂條目行為。如果需要 Blizzard 自己的檢視器設定面板，請使用 |cff60A5FA/cdm|r。",
    ["The Datatexts module addon is disabled — enable it under Modules to configure datatexts. The Info Bar's widget lists below are empty until it loads."] = "Datatexts 模組附加元件已停用 - 請在模組中啟用它以設定資料文字。資訊條的小工具清單在載入前會是空的。",
    ["The Datatexts module addon is disabled — enable it under Modules to configure datatexts. The datatext dropdowns below are empty until it loads."] = "Datatexts 模組附加元件已停用 - 請在模組中啟用它以設定資料文字。下方的資料文字下拉選單在載入前會是空的。",
    ["The HUD Visibility section controls which elements show in and out of combat."] = "HUD 可見性區段控制哪些元素在戰鬥內外顯示。",
    ["The anchoring system lets you position QUI elements relative to each other or to screen anchor points. This provides pixel-perfect control over your UI layout without needing Blizzard Edit Mode."] = "錨定系統可讓你將 QUI 元素彼此相對或相對於螢幕錨點定位。這可在不使用 Blizzard 編輯模式的情況下，精確控制 UI 版面配置。",
    ["The combat timer shows elapsed encounter time during boss fights."] = "戰鬥計時器會在首領戰中顯示已過的遭遇時間。",
    ["Theme"] = "主題",
    ["Theme & Colors"] = "主題與顏色",
    ["Theme Accent"] = "主題強調色",
    ["Theme Preset"] = "主題預設",
    ["Theme accent"] = "佈景主題強調色",
    ["These are related to WoW 12.0's combat security system. Most are harmless and self-correct after combat ends. If they persist out of combat, update to the latest QUI version or report the specific error on GitHub."] = "這些與 WoW 12.0 的戰鬥安全系統有關。多數情況無害，會在戰鬥結束後自行修正。若在非戰鬥時仍持續出現，請更新到最新 QUI 版本，或在 GitHub 回報具體錯誤。",
    ["These keybinds work everywhere: nameplates, world mouseover, or current target. Pings the unit you're looking at."] = "這些快捷鍵在任何地方都能用：姓名板、世界滑鼠指向，或目前目標。會 Ping 你正在看的單位。",
    ["These settings apply throughout the UI. Individual elements with their own font options will override these defaults."] = "這些設定套用於整個 UI。具有自己字型選項的個別元素會覆寫這些預設。",
