    ["Welcome"] = "歡迎",
    ["Welcome to QUI"] = "歡迎使用 QUI",
    ["What happens to bars when the tracked buff is not active: always show, fade to the alpha below, or hide entirely."] = "當追蹤的增益效果未啟用時，條件列會如何顯示：始終顯示、淡出到下方透明度，或完全隱藏。",
    ["What is QUI Layout Mode?"] = "什麼是 QUI 版面模式？",
    ["What is QUI?"] = "什麼是 QUI？",
    ["What is the Cooldown Manager (CDM)?"] = "什麼是冷卻管理器（CDM）？",
    ["What the Alts datatext shows on the bar: total gold across your tracked alts, or the number of tracked alts. The tooltip always lists every alt."] = "條上的「小號」資料文字顯示內容：你所有追蹤小號的總金幣，或追蹤小號的數量。提示永遠會列出每個小號。",
    ["What the Alts datatext shows on the bar: total gold across your tracked alts, or the number of tracked alts. The tooltip always lists every alt. Applies everywhere the Alts datatext is shown, including datatext panels."] = "條上的「小號」資料文字顯示內容：你所有追蹤小號的總金幣，或追蹤小號的數量。提示永遠會列出每個小號。適用於顯示小號資料文字的所有地方，包括資料文字面板。",
    ["What the alert is anchored to: the screen, the CDM Essential bar, or your focus unit frame."] = "警示錨定到哪裡：螢幕、CDM Essential 條，或你的焦點單位框架。",
    ["What this binding does: cast a spell or macro, change target/focus/assist, open the unit menu, or send a ping. Spell and Macro reveal an input below for the spell name or macro body."] = "此綁定的作用：施放法術或巨集、切換目標/焦點/協助、開啟單位選單，或送出 ping。法術與巨集會在下方顯示法術名稱或巨集內容輸入欄。",
    ["What's New"] = "最新消息",
    ["When Blizzard would open a whisper in a new window (right-click popout, or the 'open whispers in a new window' setting), open a QUI conversation tab instead."] = "當暴雪原本會用新視窗開啟密語時（右鍵彈出，或「在新視窗開啟密語」設定），改為開啟 QUI 對話分頁。",
    ["When ON (default), Healing Done / HPS sum each source's healing AND absorb shields. Turn off for pure HealingDone (matching Blizzard's stock meter)."] = "開啟時（預設），Healing Done / HPS 會把每個來源的治療量與吸收護盾都加總。關閉後則為純 HealingDone（與暴雪原生計量器一致）。",
    ["When ON (default), clear all damage-meter sessions when a Mythic+ key starts so Overall begins at zero for that run."] = "開啟時（預設），大秘境鑰石開始時清空所有傷害計量器的階段，因此 Overall 會從該場次的 0 開始。",
    ["When ON (default), hide realm names: show \"Name\" instead of \"Name-Realm\" for cross-realm players on rows, tooltips, and the breakdown popup."] = "開啟時（預設）隱藏伺服器名稱：跨伺服器玩家在列表、提示和明細彈出視窗中顯示為「名稱」，而不是「名稱-伺服器」。",
    ["When ON (default), rows show the other metric in parentheses — e.g. DPS mode shows 1.5M (42.3M). Turn off to show only the primary value."] = "開啟時（預設），列會在括號中顯示另一個數值，例如 DPS 模式顯示 1.5M (42.3M)。關閉後只顯示主要數值。",
    ["When ON, windows showing Overall switch to Current when a key starts, then Current switches back to Overall when the key completes."] = "當切換到主位置啟用時，也會隱藏主資源條，避免兩個資源同時顯示。",
    ["When Swap to Primary Position is active, also hide the primary power bar so both resources aren't shown together."] = "當切換到主位置啟用時，也會隱藏主資源條，避免兩個資源同時顯示。",
    ["When an NPC gossip has a single option, pick it automatically so you skip the popup."] = "當 NPC 對話只有單一選項時，自動選取，省去彈窗。",
    ["When an external button-skinning addon is installed, let it skin QUI's action buttons instead of QUI's built-in skin."] = "安裝外部按鈕外觀插件時，讓其替換 QUI 動作按鈕的外觀而非使用 QUI 內建外觀。",
    ["When an external button-skinning addon is installed, let it skin buff/debuff icons instead of QUI's own border."] = "安裝外部按鈕外觀插件時，讓其替換增益／減益圖示的外觀而非使用 QUI 自有邊框。",
    ["When an external button-skinning addon is installed, let it skin group-frame aura icons instead of QUI's own border."] = "安裝外部按鈕外觀插件時，讓其替換隊伍框架光環圖示的外觀而非使用 QUI 自有邊框。",
    ["When bars appear: always, only while the tracked buff/debuff is active, or only while in combat."] = "條何時出現：始終、僅在追蹤的增益/減益啟用時，或僅在戰鬥中。",
    ["When class color is off, use QUI accent color. Otherwise the custom Bar Color below is used."] = "當關閉職業色時，使用 QUI 強調色。否則使用下方自訂條色。",
    ["When enabled, the macro selections below are stored per-character instead of being shared by every character on this AceDB profile. The toggle itself is always per-character. Turning it on copies your current profile selections as a starting point."] = "啟用後，下方巨集選擇會以角色為單位儲存，而不是由此 AceDB 設定檔中的每個角色共用。切換本身永遠是角色專屬。開啟時會先複製你目前的設定檔選擇作為起點。",
    ["When hovering a dead unit, any spell binding is temporarily replaced by your class's resurrection spell if you know one. Restores the original spell when the unit is alive."] = "滑鼠指向死亡單位時，若你學會了該法術，你的任何法術綁定都會暫時改成你職業的復活法術。當單位復活後會還原原本法術。",
    ["When icons appear: always visible, only while the spell is active/on cooldown, or only while in combat."] = "圖示何時出現：始終可見、僅在法術啟用/冷卻中，或僅在戰鬥中。",
    ["When icons appear: always, only when the buff is active, or only while in combat."] = "圖示何時出現：始終、僅在增益啟用時，或僅在戰鬥中。",
    ["When on, %s messages use the days slider on the right instead of the default retention. When off, the default applies."] = "啟用時，%s 訊息改用右側的天數滑桿，而不是預設保留時間。關閉時則使用預設值。",
    ["When on, dragging only works while holding the move modifier. When off, any plain left-click drag repositions supported windows."] = "啟用時，只有按住移動修飾鍵才能拖曳。關閉時，任何普通左鍵拖曳都可重新定位支援的視窗。",
    ["When recalling a message with Up/Down, also restore its original chat type (Say, Yell, Whisper target, channel) so pressing Enter sends to the same destination."] = "用上/下鍵調出訊息時，也會還原其原始聊天類型（說、喊、密語目標、頻道），因此按 Enter 會送到相同對象。",
    ["When remaining duration drops below this, the bar switches to the Low-Time Color."] = "剩餘時間低於此值時，條會切換為低時間顏色。",
    ["When the anchor target is hidden but this frame stays visible, keep it at its last screen position instead of snapping toward the hidden anchor."] = "當錨定目標被隱藏但此框架仍可見時，保持在最後的螢幕位置，而不是朝隱藏的錨點吸附。",
    ["When the native meter is visible. Always = shown at all times; In Combat = only during combat; Hidden = meter exists but is invisible."] = "當原生計量器可見時。始終 = 一直顯示；戰鬥中 = 只在戰鬥中；隱藏 = 計量器存在但不可見。",
    ["When the primary power bar is visible (always, in combat only, when depleted, etc.)."] = "當主要資源條可見時（始終、僅在戰鬥中、耗盡時等）。",
    ["When the secondary power bar is visible (always, in combat only, when depleted, etc.)."] = "當次要資源條可見時（始終、僅在戰鬥中、耗盡時等）。",
    ["When the secondary resource is dominant for your spec, swap it into the primary bar's position for that spec."] = "當次要資源對你的專精是主導資源時，將它切到主要資源條的位置。",
    ["When the skyriding bar is shown: always on, only while flying, or auto-fade out shortly after you land."] = "當天巡條顯示時：始終開啟、僅在飛行時，或落地後自動淡出。",
    ["When to show the icon: always visible, only in combat, or only when you have a hostile target."] = "何時顯示圖示：始終可見、僅在戰鬥中，或只有在你有敵對目標時。",
    ["When to show tooltips for items in your bags and equipment. Modifier options only show the tooltip while the key is held."] = "何時顯示背包與裝備中物品的提示。修飾鍵選項只會在按住按鍵時顯示提示。",
