    ["When to show tooltips on UI frames (action bars, unit frames, etc.)."] = "何時在 UI 框架上顯示提示（動作條、單位框架等）。",
    ["When your character name contains a space (e.g., 'Foo Bar'), trigger on the first part. Most player names don't have spaces."] = "當你的角色名含有空格時（例如「Foo Bar」），會以第一部分作為觸發。多數玩家名字都沒有空格。",
    ["Where global skin borders get their color: Theme (follows your theme accent), Class (your class color), or Custom (the color picker)."] = "全域皮膚邊框的顏色來源：Theme（跟隨主題強調色）、Class（職業色），或 Custom（色彩選擇器）。",
    ["Where on the frame the %1$s indicator is anchored. X/Y Offset below nudges it from this anchor point."] = "%1$s 指示器在框架上的錨定位置。下方的 X/Y 偏移會從此錨點微調。",
