    ["Where the cast icon border gets its color: Inherit (global skin border), Theme accent, Class color, or a Custom color."] = "施放圖示邊框的顏色來源：Inherit（全域皮膚邊框）、Theme 強調色、Class 色，或自訂顏色。",
