    ["Whether the Time datatext shows your local system time or realm server time."] = "Time 資料文字顯示本機系統時間或伺服器時間。",
    ["Whether the bar drains horizontally or vertically as the aura ticks down."] = "條在光環倒數時，是水平還是垂直消耗。",
